{"tid":320283,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"肥絲和廚子 飲食台的白痴","createTime":"2017-07-13T12:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T00:23:27.000Z","uid":12458,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1dc28aeece793d6a4ec54c13cd31a10217b36f","tid":320283,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"接力"},{"pid":"b6e8cc7c0d39e71ef556e41526524dd4458fab83","tid":320283,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d877f0580addb5f587cfcb6f3dcd21b55c69b73d","tid":320283,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"加量個力呀"},{"pid":"19fb7318b5c95f9dac51b205776759a3414980db","tid":320283,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"勞斯萊斯？"},{"pid":"bb2c0dd5c05fb51b3abbb541bb517939662e2929","tid":320283,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:06:03.000Z","msg":"鄭中基嗰首天才與白痴？"},{"pid":"963b16459f06fda82639d51cf4cf68e980e3f754","tid":320283,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勞斯萊斯？</blockquote><br />\n都係吉妹醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fd4f5b29b2c3c42fe2a743de5d0f79fc6ea358","tid":320283,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"等本癲狗介紹下肥絲到底係何方神聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話到明肥絲, 緊係肥閪一條啦. 咁到底佢有幾撚肥? 不如睇下佢既自我介紹啦:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>原來男人老狗得果158CM高, 168磅!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/wg5s0sjbb/Truth_Weight.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fwg5s0sjbb%2FTruth_Weight.png&h=4237dead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得佢成日咁憎本癲狗啦, 因為本癲狗高條肥閪一截, 又冇條肥閪咁撚肥, 咁佢咪妒忌我承機攻擊我囉. 誰不知天網恢恢, 咁都俾我搵到條肥閪既自爆POST, 咁佢自己攞黎柒, 我都幫佢唔撚到啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然佢唔敢POST自己身型既相, 就等本癲狗幫佢一把啦, 男人身高158CM, 168磅既身型大慨係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/fwrlxvnrv/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Ffwrlxvnrv%2Fimage.jpg&h=1787cf3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲自爆係畜牲?</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n原來肥絲除左肥矮臭柒毒之外, 原來仲好撚似猩猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 各位睇下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/4uvmleq7p/Screenshot_2017-05-27-10-13-54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2F4uvmleq7p%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-10-13-54.png&h=0463833c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲年齡之謎&hellip;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲咁撚ON9, 大家估下佢幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哩層本癲狗都無法判斷, 請各位巴打分析下:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n84日前, 牠27歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/472926oth/27_84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2F472926oth%2F27_84.png&h=71a99850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n110日前, 牠30歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/n706uevsl/30_110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2Fn706uevsl%2F30_110.png&h=4c570172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n154日前, 牠24歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/gf9qghnsp/24_154.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fgf9qghnsp%2F24_154.png&h=0a9f11af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n170日前, 牠31歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/n1ezatkgh/31_170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fn1ezatkgh%2F31_170.png&h=92e0b647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n175日前, 牠25歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/9j52syre7/25_175.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F9j52syre7%2F25_175.png&h=7727adf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n179日前, 牠27歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.postimg.org/dulrpdl7x/27_179.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.postimg.org%2Fdulrpdl7x%2F27_179.png&h=0127f621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n180日前, 牠30歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/d7irbcnc7/30_180.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2Fd7irbcnc7%2F30_180.png&h=0a4a9f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥絲, 好心你寫野MAKE SENSE D 啦, 成日學人講邏輯, 話人唔撚夠你講, 咁宜家你又解唔解釋到哩個呀傻閪? 你都係匿番入你老母個閪扮睇唔到算啦, 無謂衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>癲狗感想:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n肥絲, 其實你做埋咁多野，大費周章，起哂我底，圖文並茂，本癲狗真係好開心架，因為好少可真係有d狗俾我撚到發哂火，非係要整鳩我不可，我的目的已經達到了<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />雖然你咁有心機整咁大篇垃圾批鬥文出黎，但來來去去都係得果幾條基佬撐你，全世界都當你傻閪，唔想理你，咁你都唔洗遷怒於我架? 你估你又好好咩? 男人老狗幻想自己係女都算，但幻想自己係d狗都唔屌既油脂肥婆，你係唔係老母中撚在幅射生到你心理變態呀? 真係人唔笑，狗都吠呀<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知你老母生到你又肥又基又弱智，現實廢鳩一條，只能做鍵盤戰士，你好憎佢，想佢日日俾人屌，但你都唔洗借本癲狗過橋架? 你老母做雞，我已經盡量幫襯多d，屌到佢閪皮都化埋，你唔洗再引其他人屌佢啦，做人唔好咁撚不孝先得架<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係因為你自小就因為肥矮臭柒毒所以俾人排斥, 冇朋友, 冇人注意, 所以一上網就要做鍵盤戰士, 引人注意, 認為嘈交贏左就係&quot;打贏仗&quot;, 將自己開既post叫做&quot;戰場&quot;. 可惜, 你對住本癲狗就從來都未贏過一仗, 連自己自以為擅長既地方都俾人打敗, 唔怪得你咁憎我啦. <img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8731c02a650c23628d9011a33cf67b25ce2655b0","tid":320283,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"肥絲原是個假膠垃圾不止"},{"pid":"23891ad80cdcb8b909132e6bbd50dd690c771db3","tid":320283,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"廚子柒左又唔認輸"},{"pid":"4edcb5a2c4d1282078f125d892e6774bdc52f840","tid":320283,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42d70c25bd64bdbae6f364ba07b1ea890ce8a2e1","tid":320283,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"兩條垃圾私怨撚煩到死，BLOCK咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6b1c7f7dd1dfb9c2ba09f3b4586d124502ea7f","tid":320283,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"偏偏 他倆撤夜纏綿"},{"pid":"11f60370ae0987e56308760d752583ddb9d55442","tid":320283,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"我有冇改錯歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6017c7d75262d4296f820462ad75956a51716b20","tid":320283,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"每日慣性發作 延誤就醫"},{"pid":"ab68aad85ec057b3c5ffe1449ccdc776a9f57b1d","tid":320283,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n又開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死敵"},{"pid":"cca4fb81c94f3cff6e1891e70146a86b44e1f90f","tid":320283,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"下一句有啲難改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打接力"},{"pid":"886282062ace2f404d4414ca4744969144109cf2","tid":320283,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:50:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6ededf59db7d00750d5377511b0256be0b35787","tid":320283,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚憎個死肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持癲狗巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753fdeb72de47d043faf30f51fd66e8b4f05f19c","tid":320283,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廚子柒左又唔認輸</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n癲狗我坐船頭，肥閪你岸鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}